These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, dancing, singing, woodworking
4 different pets are kept: bird, goldfish, guinea-pig, fish
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, brazilian, mexican, indonesian
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, iced-tea, fanta, almond-milk
 1. the brazilian is not to the right of the colombian##8
 2. the person drinking milk is not to the left of the person drinking milk##8
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the colombian is not to the left of the indonesian##8
 5. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the person drinking milk##8
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the indonesian##1
 7. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##5
 8. the owner of the fish is between the person drinking iced-tea and the brazilian##2
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
10. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
11. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
13. the owner of the guinea-pig is not to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##8
14. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person drinking fanta##1
15. the person who's hobby is dancing is not the brazilian##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | camping     | dancing   | woodworking | singing |
| Pet   | goldfish | fish   | bird   | guinea-pig  |
| Nationality         | brazilian  | mexican  | indonesian  | colombian |
| Beverage     | milk    | fanta | iced-tea     | almond-milk    |

