.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, milk, sprite, water
City: boston, nizza, liverpool, london
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, librarian, writer, fisherman
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, azalea, daffodil, iris
 1. the writer is between the person who growsballoon-flower and the librarian##2
 2. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the person who growsazalea##8
 3. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3
 4. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the person who growsiris##8
 5. the person who growsballoon-flower is not to the left of the librarian##8
 6. the person traveling to london is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
 7. the person who growsdaffodil is somewhere to the left of the person who growsiris##5
 8. the person who growsdaffodil is in an odd position##4
 9. the designer is the person who growsazalea##1
10. the writer is on the left or right of the person who growsballoon-flower##3
11. the person who growsballoon-flower is not to the left of the writer##8
12. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
13. the fisherman is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to nizza##5
14. the librarian is on the left or right of the writer##3
15. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
17. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the librarian##8
18. the person traveling to nizza is not to the right of the person who growsazalea##8
19. the person drinking water is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | lemonade | sprite | water  | milk  |
| City          | london     | nizza | boston | liverpool  |
| Job   | librarian    | writer  | fisherman | designer |
| Flower           | daffodil | iris | balloon-flower    | azalea  |

