City: rome, paris, new-york, venice
House: colonial, modern, gothic-revival, townhouse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, sailing, surfing
 1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
 2. the person who likes orange is somewhere to the right of the person who likes purple##5
 3. the person who likes blood-red is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to venice##5
 4. the person who likes purple is somewhere to the right of the colonial house##5
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the right of the person traveling to rome##8
 6. the person who likes blood-red is not to the left of the person traveling to new-york##8
 7. the gothic-revival house is in an odd position##4
 8. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
 9. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
11. the person traveling to rome is not to the left of the modern house##8
12. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Color         | fuchsia    | blood-red   | purple | orange |
| City   | rome     | new-york  | venice   | paris      |
| House   | modern | colonial    | gothic-revival      | townhouse       |
| Sport         | sailing    | climbing | surfing   | cycling    |

