 2. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the fonseca-smoker##3
 3. the person driving the train is the person drinking water##1
 4. the person driving the boat is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking sprite##2
 5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the davidoff-smoker##3
 6. the davidoff-smoker is not to the right of the person driving the boat##8
 7. the person who's hobby is reading is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
 9. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
10. the person drinking sprite is the davidoff-smoker##1
11. the bongani-smoker is not to the right of the person driving the scooter##8
12. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the bongani-smoker##3
13. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
14. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the bongani-smoker##3
15. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
