 3. the person playing poker is not to the left of the person drinking water##8
 4. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
 5. the person playing mah-jongg is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##8
 7. the person drinking sprite is not the person who's sport is cricket##6
 8. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere between the person playing mah-jongg and the person drinking sprite##7
 9. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in march##5
10. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
11. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
12. the person who's birthday is in march is not the person who's sport is ice-hockey##6
13. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
14. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
15. the person playing poker is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in march##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4     |
