 7. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
 8. the townhouse house is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 9. the person eating eggplant is somewhere to the left of the person watching western movies##5
10. the person watching western movies is on the right of the modern house##1
11. the person eating watermelon is on the far left or far right##3
12. the person eating blueberry is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
13. the wooden house is not to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##8
14. the person who's sport is parkour is not to the right of the person who's sport is surfing##8
15. the person who's sport is parkour is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
16. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the right of the person watching western movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3     |    4    |
| Sport           | basketball | parkour       | swimming      | surfing  |
| Movie-Genre   | action    | martial-arts | western   | drama   |
